  <description><![CDATA[<p>This one’s for the foodies! We’ve planned a four-night tour where you’ll get to taste the region’s best food, with lunch in an agritourismo, a cooking class, wine tasting and a culinary walking tour – all with the beautiful backdrop of the <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amalfi Coast</a>. You’ll get to explore the stunning coastlines and the pastel coloured towns of the Campania region – trying fresh local food as you go. In this part of Italy is famous for it’s sweet, aromatic Amalfi lemons, deliciously creamy buffalo mozzarella and juicy sun ripened tomatoes, you’ll be in the perfect place for a foodie adventure.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/flavours-of-the-amalfi-coast#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/flavours-of-the-amalfi-coast#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/flavours-of-the-amalfi-coast#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/flavours-of-the-amalfi-coast#Hotels">Hotels</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/flavours-of-the-amalfi-coast#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
